        <mxCell id="rule" value="Rule of thumb: AI tools surface candidates; PubMed validates them. Never cite a paper an LLM gave you without checking the PMID." style="text;html=1;align=center;fontSize=11;fontStyle=2;fontColor=#A83732;" vertex="1" parent="1">
