        <mxCell id="rule2" value="LLMs (ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini) without a retrieval layer are particularly prone to inventing plausible-looking citations." style="text;html=1;align=center;fontSize=9;fontColor=#76716B;" vertex="1" parent="1">
